/* 

Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)
Approach:
1. Split list into two lists:
  a → nodes at odd positions
  b → nodes at even positions
2. Reverse the even list (b).
3. Attach reversed b at the end of a

*/




/*
